Insider Activity


Individual




I. Edgar Hendrix



Mr. I. E. Hendrix is Independent Director at Matrix Service Co. He is on the Board of Directors at Matrix Service Co. and Cherokee Nation Enterprises LLC.
Mr. Hendrix was previously employed as Chairman by Beta Operating Co. LLC, President by Patriot Energy Resources, Inc., Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President by Loudfire, Inc., Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President by Atlas Pipeline Mid-Continent LLC, Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President by Spectrum Field Services, Inc., Treasurer & Vice President by Parker Drilling Co., and a Trustee by Cavanal Hill Funds. He also served on the board at Whitmar Exploration Co.
He received his undergraduate degree from Oklahoma Christian University and an MBA from the University of Oklahoma.



