Brown, Tony (1992). Jimi Hendrix: A Visual Documentary - His Life, Loves and Music. Omnibus Press. ISBN 978-0-7119-2761-2. 
Brown, Tony (1997). Jimi Hendrix: The Final Days. Omnibus Press. ISBN 978-0-7119-5238-6. 
